final_desc: - - Lobster (Homarus spp.) :Krustasea, berkulit maupun tidak, hidup, segar, dingin, beku, dikeringkan, diasinkan atau dalam air garam; krustasea diasapi, dimasak maupun tidak sebelum atau selama proses pengasapan; krustasea, berkulit, dikukus atau direbus, dingin, beku, dikeringkan, diasinkan atau dalam air garam maupun tidak; tepung, tepung kasar dan pellet dari krustasea, layak untuk dikonsumsi manusia.;- - Lobsters (Homarus spp.) :Crustaceans, whether in shell or not, live, fresh, chilled, frozen, dried, salted or in brine; smoked crustaceans, whether in shell or not, whether or not cooked before or during the smoking process; crustaceans, in shell, cooked by steaming or by boiling in water, whether or not chilled, frozen, dried, salted or in brine; flours, meals and pellets of crustaceans, fit for human consumption.;- - Frogs' legs- - Kaki kodok

- - Udang dan udang besar air dingin (Pandalus spp, Crangon crangon) :Krustasea, berkulit maupun tidak, hidup, segar, dingin, beku, dikeringkan, diasinkan atau dalam air garam; krustasea diasapi, dimasak maupun tidak sebelum atau selama proses pengasapan; krustasea, berkulit, dikukus atau direbus, dingin, beku, dikeringkan, diasinkan atau dalam air garam maupun tidak; tepung, tepung kasar dan pellet dari krustasea, layak untuk dikonsumsi manusia.;- - Cold-water shrimps and prawns (Pandalus spp., Crangon crangon) :Crustaceans, whether in shell or not, live, fresh, chilled, frozen, dried, salted or in brine; smoked crustaceans, whether in shell or not, whether or not cooked before or during the smoking process; crustaceans, in shell, cooked by steaming or by boiling in water, whether or not chilled, frozen, dried, salted or in brine; flours, meals and pellets of crustaceans, fit for human consumption.;- - Other- - Lain-lain
